<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>동구의 희망, 박미경 - 30년 현장 전문가</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        .hero-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
        }
        .pledge-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        /* 드라이브 미리보기를 위한 컨테이너 스타일 */
        .drive-embed-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .drive-embed-container iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">

    <!-- 네비게이션 -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black text-blue-700">박미경</div>
            <div class="space-x-6 text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">
                <a href="#about" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">소개</a>
                <a href="#video" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">영상</a>
                <a href="#pledge" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">공약</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 히어로 섹션 -->
    <header class="hero-gradient text-white pt-24 pb-36 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-blue-900/40 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border border-white/20">30년 의료·돌봄 현장 전문가</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
                동구의 삶을 바꿀<br>단 하나의 선택, 박미경
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl opacity-90 font-light leading-relaxed">
                "말이 아닌 실행으로, 결과로 보답하겠습니다."
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 -mt-24">
        <!-- 사진 섹션 -->
        <section id="about" class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
            <!-- 사진 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl">
                <div class="aspect-[3/4] drive-embed-container shadow-inner">
                    <iframe src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KQOaljZaZgYPGlSJEIEhp2r-0bHkDl7w/preview"></iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 text-center">
                    <p class="text-blue-700 font-bold mb-1">현장 전문가</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">시민의 삶을 직접 겪어온 30년</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 사진 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl">
                <div class="aspect-[3/4] drive-embed-container shadow-inner">
                    <iframe src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FxhuUB1KjratMORa2tFvf6vLHKolwQCM/preview"></iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 text-center">
                    <p class="text-blue-700 font-bold mb-1">준비된 후보</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">동구의 내일을 책임질 리더십</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 후보 인사말 -->
        <section class="mb-24 text-center px-4">
            <div class="inline-block w-16 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mb-10"></div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-10 text-gray-800">"동구의 돌봄을 하나로 연결하겠습니다"</h2>
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6 font-medium bg-white p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
                <p>30년 의료·돌봄 현장에서 시민의 삶을 직접 겪어온 박미경입니다.</p>
                <p>동구의 돌봄은 아직도 따로 움직이고 있습니다.</p>
                <p class="text-blue-700 font-extrabold text-2xl md:text-3xl bg-blue-50 py-4 rounded-2xl">
                    의료·복지·돌봄을 연결하는 통합돌봄으로<br class="hidden md:block"> 사각지대를 없애겠습니다.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 동영상 섹션 -->
        <section id="video" class="mb-24">
            <div class="text-center mb-10">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">박미경의 진심, 영상으로 확인하세요</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video relative border-8 border-white">
                <iframe 
                    src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jOby79Tbagj8kLuCYO5M-ImqYN0bcxUy/preview" 
                    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" 
                    allow="autoplay"
                    allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 공약 섹션 -->
        <section id="pledge" class="mb-24 px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-800">박미경의 3대 핵심 약속</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="pledge-card bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100 shadow-xl text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 mx-auto mb-8 text-3xl">🤝</div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 text-blue-800 leading-tight">통합돌봄 완성</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">의료·복지·돌봄을 연결하여 단 한 명의 소외되는 이웃도 없는 동구를 만들겠습니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="pledge-card bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100 shadow-xl text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600 mx-auto mb-8 text-3xl">👵</div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 text-green-800 leading-tight">촘촘한 복지</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">어르신과 취약계층의 삶을 현장에서 직접 챙기며 놓치지 않고 지원하겠습니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="pledge-card bg-white p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-gray-100 shadow-xl text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-orange-100 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 mx-auto mb-8 text-3xl">🏠</div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-black mb-4 text-orange-800 leading-tight">안전한 주거</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">누구나 안전하고 쾌적하게 살 수 있는 동구, 누구나 부러워하는 동구를 만들겠습니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 마지막 인사 -->
        <section class="bg-blue-700 rounded-[3rem] p-16 text-center text-white mb-20 shadow-2xl shadow-blue-200">
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl opacity-90 mb-6 font-light">"현장의 경험으로 결과로 보답하겠습니다"</p>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-10 leading-tight">이번 선택, 박미경에게 맡겨주십시오</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                <button class="bg-white text-blue-700 px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-black text-2xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-lg">
                    박미경 지지하기
                </button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-500 py-16 px-6 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto border-t border-gray-800 pt-10">
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-400 mb-2">기호 X번 박미경 후보 캠프</p>
            <p class="mb-4">© 2026 박미경 후보. 모든 권리는 후보자에게 있습니다.</p>
            <p class="text-xs opacity-50">본 웹사이트는 제공된 공약을 바탕으로 제작된 공식 홍보 페이지입니다.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
